replies.body:
NinjaGuy with the assist! {{summoner:31}} 

Those legacy/limited skins don't ever have a set time when they come back, but The Harrowing would be a pretty good time to look for Reaper Soraka! You should also check out the [**sales page**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/store/sales) from time to time to see if they're on the way back to the store. 

P.S. Hextech crafting and mystery gifting should also have her as a possible reward. You could get lucky and score her skin that way!
